                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5448" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0815</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8331 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">逢“新”化吉？新租赁准则对吉祥航空财务报表和租赁决策的影响</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Will it turn bad into luck? The impact of New Leasing Standard on Juneyao Airlines’ financial statements and leasing decisions</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐晓霞，王丽娟，石恒贵，陈煦江</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海吉祥航空股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉祥航空；新租赁准则 ；经营租赁；飞机租赁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Juneyao Airlines; New Lease Standards; Operating Lease; Aircraft Lease</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">租赁作为企业重要的融资渠道，近年来被很多企业加以利用，实现表外融资。为了保证财务报表信息的真实性和可比性，财政部于2018年发布《企业会计准则第21号——租赁》，要求承租人采用单一的租赁模型，将经营租赁纳入报表核算范围，并规定执行企业会计准则的企业于2021年1月1日开始实施。拥有较高租赁比例的航空运输业受租赁准则变更的影响较大，本案例结合吉祥航空的基本情况，采用新租赁准则对吉祥航空2019年的报表项目进行调整，以期发现新准则对吉祥航空的财务影响，以及在新准则下应如何做好飞机的购买与租赁决策。本案例将有助于学员掌握新租赁准则的变化原因和内容，启发学员思考新租赁准则的应对方案，增强学生的分析决策能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As an important financing channel for enterprises, leasing has been used by many enterprises to realize off-balance sheet financing in recent years. In order to ensure the authenticity and comparability of financial statement information, the Ministry of Finance issued the Accounting Standards for Business Enterprises No. 21 -- Lease in 2018, requiring lessee to adopt a single lease model and include operating lease in the accounting scope of financial statements, and stipulating that enterprises implementing the accounting standards for Business Enterprises shall start to implement it on January 1, 2021. The air transport industry has a higher proportion of leasing are greatly influenced by the change of lease criterion and combining with the basic situation of the airline in this case, the new lease criterion for the airline to adjust the report project in 2019, in order to find the new criteria on the airline&#39;s financial impact, and under the new guidelines should be how to do aircraft purchase and leasing decision. This case will help students to understand the reasons and contents of the changes of the new lease criteria, inspire students to think about the new lease criteria, and enhance students&#39; analytical and decision-making ability.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》、《财务管理理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新久租赁准则</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
